title: FULL SHOW: We Chat With Tory Lanez, Noah Kerner, PnB Rock Updates and More
itunes:title: FULL SHOW: We Chat With Tory Lanez, Noah Kerner, PnB Rock Updates and More
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club we got R&B Singer Tory Lanez coming to talk about his new album "Sorry 4 What" and later we have Acorn CEO Noah Kerner join us. During the Rumor Report, Yee discusses the latest in the PnB Rock murder and who got charged...
